column1: IF ccr_sb_oh_f_d is MF 0 AND ccr_s_at_d is MF 0 AND ccr_etio_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
IF ccr_testosterone_d is MF 2 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1
IF  THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_b_cortolone_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 0
IF ccr_thf_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
